          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1080.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>walnuts</strong> finely</p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>sultanas</strong> finely</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
